Interface IJobEvent<Job extends BaseRetryPolicyAwareJob,Result>

    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface IJobEvent<Job extends BaseRetryPolicyAwareJob,Result>
extends IEvent<Result>
    JobEvent is posted on the de.greenrobot.event.EventBus returned by IServiceSupport.getEventBus() in order to notify interested listeners of changes in SDK state or data availability as a direct result of executing a BaseRetryPolicyAwareJob
